lass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T09:59:07.000Z","msg":"可唔可以介紹吓"},{"pid":"7a1d615e1dd30654196f6c8570dd8e5d83b0fd29","tid":595962,"uid":16697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6b59838a60c67ab0c6eb72a1c178b179bd3b424b","tid":595962,"uid":20134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T08:14:24.000Z","msg":"下爬左右位置多唔多瘡？<br />\n有冇成日口苦/心煩之類？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T10:05:53.000Z","msg":"巴打我腮位左右二邊都有，咩來點醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ceda8edab46a15cc0d468621f3dfd6582f1c524","tid":595962,"uid":74315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T10:10:20.000Z","msg":"你係食a酸前已有定食完先有？<br />\n我又係食完療程後尾枕生得好勁<br />\n但我以前係冇"},{"pid":"bd43c831b193e7746c081da88ff5cafdb6b31722","tid":595962,"uid":12850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T10:17:06.000Z","msg":"一日打幾多次飛機"},{"pid":"14ae89958f22619392d31f98d285a6620c0fe4e4","tid":595962,"uid":125072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"294da0391672a5d55e55bc15cd33d82a69bf13e0","tid":595962,"uid":101928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"527ae9c950e31ad2fcf03b4fa25305d0adb75ff9","tid":595962,"uid":125072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T09:41:07.000Z","msg":"以前成日都會生頭瘡<br />\n冇巴打咁嚴重<br />\n但長期都Keep住有幾粒咁<br />\n不過用咗手工洗髮皂之後就幾乎冇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T09:59:07.000Z","msg":"可唔可以介紹吓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T10:33:42.000Z","msg":"其實我最初係因為脫髮問題先會開始用手工皂嘅<br />\n雖然一路都有頭瘡 但因為唔算太嚴重所以都冇乜點為意<br />\n點知用咗一排手工皂之後突然發現自己啲頭瘡冇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依加諗番應該係因為本身對市面啲洗頭水敏感<br />\n轉用手工皂之後少接觸咗嗰啲化學成份所以先會好番<br />\n不過對於本身頭皮有問題嘅巴絲可能就冇乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但幾十蚊一舊我覺得都值得一試嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b26d3e41387336577d2ab344681dc1de76edd6ee","tid":595962,"uid":81354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"872427285123131a6f77358abf2803bb63bcca03","tid":595962,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3227dfa518cd95bab606029f1954a38f12803535","tid":595962,"uid":54758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12a067bda157f09434a0f302ce6c9885b779f989","tid":595962,"uid":81354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T09:20:08.000Z","msg":"我都有頭瘡。睇左次醫生話冇計，係油脂分泌旺盛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我只可以一路食藥，唔食就會生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T09:23:59.000Z","msg":"食抗生素定食a酸？<br />\n持續生頭瘡 頭髮會唔會越黎越少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T09:34:44.000Z","msg":"我發現我髮尾都有啲暗瘡疤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T10:33:53.000Z","msg":"抗生素 會，所以即使長期食藥實對身體有小小負擔我都唔敢唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90c2c6983efffdf606b25c1b899777d6219b7a6","tid":595962,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T10:36:24.000Z","msg":"轉洗頭水"},{"pid":"9581d581945e647d5417523d3285c161f582825a","tid":595962,"uid":57848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T10:41:46.000Z","msg":"我以前都有頭瘡，間唔時會番發，可以透過幾招搞掂。<br />\n<br />\n你可唔可以剷走後面啲髮腳？剷走後用洗頭水捽多幾下就得。<br />\n<br />\n你用番啲無矽洗頭水，洗完太乾就補少少護髮素。不過唔好洗太密，一日最多一次，唔係太乾又係會油。<br />\n<br />\n勤換枕頭套，一星期一次，幫助都好大。<br />\n<br />\n希望你早日康復！"},{"pid":"3c0f7565749b1616db9f30fb1a243d371c9ba0d2","tid":595962,"uid":82341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:26:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4254f8d6031ddbb27f3ba7af1cb02ecd5e934a94","tid":595962,"uid":43901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201